<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        @page { margin: 0.5cm; }

        :root {
            --card-primary: {$theme['primary']};
            --card-secondary: {$theme['secondary']};
            --card-text: {$theme['text']};
            --card-muted: {$theme['muted']};
            --card-border: {$theme['border']};
            --card-surface: {$theme['surface']};
            --card-bg: {$theme['background']};
            --card-on-primary: {$theme['onPrimary']};
            --card-on-secondary: {$theme['onSecondary']};
        }

        body {
            font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding-top: 2cm;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            color: var(--card-text);
        }

        .print-container {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card-wrapper {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .card {
            width: 54mm;
            height: 85.6mm;
            background: var(--card-surface);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 0.5pt dashed var(--card-border);
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .arc-blue {
            position: absolute;
            top: -15mm;
            left: -10mm;
            width: 45mm;
            height: 35mm;
            background: var(--card-primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .arc-red {
            position: absolute;
            top: -10mm;
            right: -15mm;
            width: 50mm;
            height: 30mm;
            background: var(--card-secondary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            padding: 5mm 3mm;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .content-front {
            padding-bottom: 18mm;
        }

        .logo-row {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .logo-cell {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 33.33%;
            height: 6mm;
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .logo-img {
            max-width: 13mm;
            max-height: 6mm;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .front-footer {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 3mm;
            padding: 0 2mm;
        }

        .name {
            color: var(--card-primary);
            font-size: 9pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 5mm;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            line-height: 1.15;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.6mm 1.3mm;
            border-radius: 1.2mm;
            background: var(--card-surface);
        }

        .role {
            font-size: 6.8pt;
            color: var(--card-muted);
            margin-bottom: 2mm;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .photo {
            width: 21mm;
            height: 21mm;
            margin: 0 auto 2mm;
            border: 1mm solid var(--card-primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: var(--card-surface);
        }

        .photo img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .photo-fallback {
            font-size: 6pt;
            color: var(--card-muted);
            line-height: 21mm;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .org {
            font-size: 4.8pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 2mm;
            padding: 0 2mm;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--card-text);
        }

        .id-info {
            font-size: 6.4pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 2mm;
            line-height: 1.2;
            color: var(--card-text);
        }

        .qr {
            width: 13mm;
            height: 13mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 0.25pt solid var(--card-border);
            background: var(--card-surface);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .qr img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .qr-fallback {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 5pt;
            color: var(--card-muted);
            line-height: 13mm;
        }

        .web {
            position: static;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 5.5pt;
            color: var(--card-primary);
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 1mm;
        }

        .back-qr-wrap {
            margin: 0 auto 2mm;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .back-qr-label {
            margin: 0 0 0.8mm;
            font-size: 4.8pt;
            color: var(--card-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.2pt;
        }

        .back-title {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--card-primary);
            margin-top: 10mm;
            margin-bottom: 3mm;
        }

        .back-text {
            font-size: 6.1pt;
            text-align: justify;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 5mm;
            padding: 0 4mm;
            color: var(--card-text);
        }

        .v-box {
            border: 0.3mm solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 2mm;
            padding: 1.5mm;
            width: 70%;
            margin: 0 auto 4mm;
            background: var(--card-surface);
        }

        .v-label {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 5pt;
            color: var(--card-muted);
        }

        .v-value {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 9pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--card-primary);
        }

        .sign-area {
            margin-top: 1mm;
            background: var(--card-surface);
            border-radius: 2mm;
            padding: 1mm 1mm 0.8mm;
            border: 0.25pt solid var(--card-border);
        }

        .sign-name {
            font-size: 7.5pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--card-text);
        }

        .sign-role {
            font-size: 5.5pt;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--card-muted);
        }

        .hash {
            font-size: 3.5pt;
            color: var(--card-muted);
            margin-top: 2pt;
            word-break: break-all;
            padding: 0 5mm;
            line-height: 1.15;
        }

        .meta {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 4mm;
            width: calc(100% - 4mm);
            left: 2mm;
            font-size: 4.8pt;
            color: var(--card-text);
            line-height: 1.2;
            padding: 0.8mm 1.4mm;
            border-radius: 1.6mm;
            background: var(--card-surface);
            border: 0.25pt solid var(--card-border);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="print-container">
    <p style="font-size: 10pt; color: {$theme['muted']}; margin-bottom: 1cm;">Guia de impresion: recorte por la linea punteada.</p>

    <div class="card-wrapper">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="arc-blue"></div>
            <div class="arc-red"></div>
            <div class="content content-front">

                <div class="name">{$holder['fullName']}</div>
                <div class="role">{$holder['cargo']}</div>

                <div class="photo">
                    {if !empty($holder['photoSrc'])}
                        <img src="{$holder['photoSrc']|noescape}" alt="Foto">
                    {else}
                        <p class="photo-fallback">SIN FOTO</p>
                    {/if}
                </div>

                <div class="org">{$organization}</div>

                <div class="id-info">
                    IMSS: {$holder['imss']}<br>
                    Vigencia: {$holder['vigencia']}
                </div>

                <div class="front-footer">
                    <div class="logo-row">
                        <div class="logo-cell">
                            {if !empty($logos['tecnm'])}
                                <img src="{$logos['tecnm']|noescape}" alt="TecNM" class="logo-img">
                            {/if}
                        </div>
                        <div class="logo-cell">
                            {if !empty($logos['itsm'])}
                                <img src="{$logos['itsm']|noescape}" alt="ITSM" class="logo-img">
                            {/if}
                        </div>
                        <div class="logo-cell">
                            {if !empty($logos['siut'])}
                                <img src="{$logos['siut']|noescape}" alt="SIUT" class="logo-img">
                            {/if}
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="web">{$website}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 8pt; color: {$theme['muted']};">Anverso</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-wrapper">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="arc-blue" style="top: auto; bottom: -18mm; left: -12mm;"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="back-title">Acreditacion</div>

                <div class="back-text">
                    Se acredita que la persona titular de esta credencial pertenece al padron de afiliados del
                    <strong>{$organization}</strong>.
                </div>

                <div class="v-box">
                    <p class="v-label">Vigencia</p>
                    <p class="v-value">{$holder['vigencia']}</p>
                </div>

                <div class="back-qr-wrap">
                    <p class="back-qr-label">Validacion en linea</p>
                    <div class="qr">
                        {if !empty($qrSrc)}
                            <img src="{$qrSrc|noescape}" alt="QR">
                        {else}
                            <p class="qr-fallback">SIN QR</p>
                        {/if}
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="sign-area">
                    <p class="sign-name">{$signatory['name']}</p>
                    <p class="sign-role">{$signatory['role']}</p>
                    <div class="hash">Firma digital (hash CURP): {$signatory['signatureHash']}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="meta">
                    Emision: {$issuedAt}<br>
                    {$address}<br>
                    RFC: {$rfc}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 8pt; color: {$theme['muted']};">Reverso</p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>